      <title>GQG Partners 削减 Nvidia 持股以进行风险管理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/gqg-partners-cuts-back-nvidia-holdings-for-risk-management</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资组合经理 Brian Kersmanc 表示，作为风险管理策略的一部分，GQG Partners LLC 已削减了对 Nvidia Corp. 股票的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/gqg-partners-cuts-back-nvidia-holdings-for-risk-management</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 05:05:27 GMT</pubDate>
