    <item>
      <title>日本 Sakura Internet 为数据中心项目部署 Nvidia 设备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/japan-s-sakura-internet-loads-up-on-nvidia-gear-for-data-center-project</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Sakura Internet Inc. 即将建成的数据中心很可能在三年内投入使用时就被预订一空，这将促使日本政府的本土网络提供商加大对 Nvidia Corp. 图形处理器的购买力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/japan-s-sakura-internet-loads-up-on-nvidia-gear-for-data-center-project</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 04:20:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万国数据为中国境外数据中心运营筹集 10 亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/gds-raises-1-billion-for-data-center-operations-outside-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[万国数据控股有限公司从主要为美国新投资者那里筹集了 10 亿美元，用于其在中国大陆以外的数据中心业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/gds-raises-1-billion-for-data-center-operations-outside-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 04:16:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Axis Bank 称，人工智能不会因增加一线员工而导致失业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/axis-bank-says-ai-won-t-mean-job-losses-as-it-adds-frontliners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Axis Bank Ltd. 表示，人工智能将改变工作性质，但不会导致该印度银行的净失业，该银行近年来数字化员工数量增加了 10 倍以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/axis-bank-says-ai-won-t-mean-job-losses-as-it-adds-frontliners</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Visa、Coinbase 提供通过借记卡实时购买加密货币的服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/visa-coinbase-offer-real-time-crypto-purchases-via-debit-cards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[通过支付巨头和加密货币交易所宣布的合作，持有符合条件的借记卡的 Visa Inc. 客户将能够将资金存入他们的 Coinbase Global Inc. 账户——有时是立即存入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/visa-coinbase-offer-real-time-crypto-purchases-via-debit-cards</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 00:41:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 与博通合作开发 AI 推理芯片</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/openai-broadcom-working-to-develop-ai-chip-focused-on-inference</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两位知情人士透露，OpenAI 正在与博通公司合作开发一种新型人工智能芯片，专门用于运行经过训练的人工智能模型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/openai-broadcom-working-to-develop-ai-chip-focused-on-inference</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 22:27:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能芯片增长未能激发投资者兴趣，AMD 股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/amd-forecast-falls-short-suggesting-a-slower-pace-of-ai-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[超威半导体公司 (Advanced Micro Devices Inc.) 股价在尾盘交易中下跌，此前该芯片制造商的营收预测不及分析师预期，这表明其人工智能销售增长速度低于一些人的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/amd-forecast-falls-short-suggesting-a-slower-pace-of-ai-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 20:18:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Snap 业绩增长表明广告改革正在奏效</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/snap-drops-after-projecting-slower-holiday-advertising-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Snap Inc. 公布的第三季度收入略高于分析师预期，表明其广告业务改革正在受到营销人员的青睐。该公司股价在盘后交易中上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/snap-drops-after-projecting-slower-holiday-advertising-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 20:12:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Alphabet 押注人工智能，云计算和搜索业务获得回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/alphabet-beats-quarterly-sales-estimates-on-google-cloud-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[谷歌母公司 Alphabet Inc. 周二表示，其进军人工智能领域的昂贵投资开始获得回报，其云计算业务取得了好于预期的增长，并推动了其旗舰搜索引擎的使用率上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/alphabet-beats-quarterly-sales-estimates-on-google-cloud-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 20:11:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
